title: Puppet DB Status
agents: linux
catalog: app/puppet
license: GPL
distribution: arsoft
description:
 This checks the status of the puppet DB.

perfdata:
 Number of successful and failed services.

item:
  The item {daemon} shows the daemon status.

  The item {memory} shows the memory status.

  The item {threads} shows the thread status.

  The item {queue} shows the queue status.

  The item {database} shows the queue status.

inventory:
  Returns five checks for each machine: {daemon}, {memory}, {threads},
  {queue} and {database}.
